Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:06.37,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,A city of monsters, home to a \Nslime that bested the Orc Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.98,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,Can this be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.94,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.56,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,I simply can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.06,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:21.76,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,This slime called Rimuru has saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:24.06,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.71,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of relationship \Nshould we seek with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.76,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,And should we do so on the assumption \Nthat this slime is benevolent,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.60,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,or should we perceive him as a threat \Nand attempt to eliminate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:38.27,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,You speak of eliminating him so \Neasily, but is it even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:42.61,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you an honest answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.24,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even need to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:50.49,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we should go and meet him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:55.25,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,I will judge this Rimuru \Nwith my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.17,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:02.05,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go see \Nthis slime you three met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.01,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,That {\c&H471E13&}Time {\c&HCD9612&}I Got {\c&H471E13&}Reincarnated {\c&HCD9612&}as a {\c&H7E4F0A&}Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:38.27,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1362,561)}Episode 17: The Gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.68,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.27,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I love all the food in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.28,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.28,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Were you okay yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.81,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about! Iâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.84,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,...am quite tough, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.04,Main,Minion,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sir Gabiru for you! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Did your communication crystal work okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.98,Main,Vesta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was able to contact King Gazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:12.05,Main,Vesta,0000,0000,0000,,I informed him that the Demon Lord Milim \Nattacked and you dealt with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.19,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:16.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just see how things \Ngo with Milim for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to give me a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.18,Main,Vesta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.69,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rimuru-sama's healing potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.69,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,99% of its composition is \Nextracted from hipokute herbs.
